《'''親近你'''》（{{lang-en|''Just Wanna Be Close to You''}}）是香港歌手[[黎明|黎明]]的第二張粵語[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]，全碟由[[陳永明_(音樂人)|陳永明]]監製，於1991年1月11日由唱片公司[[寶麗金|寶麗金]]首次發行，專輯在推出後半個月內已獲得雙白金銷量（十萬張以上）<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.881903.com/highlight/2374320/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/1%E6%9C%8811%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|title = 1月11日之廣東歌|date = 2021-01-10|publisher = 商業電台|language = zh|accessdate = 2021-06-05|archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210605012624if_/https://www.881903.com/highlight/2374320/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/1%E6%9C%8811%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|archive-date = 2021-06-05|dead-url = no}}</ref>，黎明憑主打歌曲之一的〈如果這是情〉首次於《[[勁歌金曲優秀選|勁歌金曲季選]]》獲獎<ref>{{Cite book | author = 林玉鑫| title = 百歌爭嗚 成名曲、流行曲快樂大放送|location = 北京|publisher = 海潮出版社| date =2001-01| pages = 371| ISBN = 7801512839|language =zh-hans}}</ref>。

==製作與發行==
《親近你》以黎明的半身照為封面主題，後面背景為一男一女在沙灘上漫步<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 劉存孝 |url = http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1939912/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A-%E9%BB%8E%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E7%99%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%89%8D%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E5%9B%9E%E9%9F%B3%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%B6-%E5%8A%89%E5%AD%98%E5%AD%9D |title = 黎天王登基前力作 |publisher = 星島日報 |date = 2019-01-04 |accessdate = 2021-05-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191007115018/http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1939912/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A-%E9%BB%8E%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E7%99%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%89%8D%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E5%9B%9E%E9%9F%B3%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%B6-%E5%8A%89%E5%AD%98%E5%AD%9D |archive-date = 2019-10-07 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，專輯收錄了10首歌曲，包括[[電視廣播有限公司|電視廣播有限公司]]當時正在播放的電視連續劇《[[人在邊緣|人在邊緣]]》的同名主題曲及插曲〈如果這是情〉<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%971-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%83%85-%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E9%BD%8A%EF%BD%8A%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-f3babba57beb|title = 《如果這是情》開展全民一齊Ｊ黎明的時代|author = 朱米高|date = 2018-07-29|publisher = 千千闋歌與我常在|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201204201201/https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%971-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%83%85-%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E9%BD%8A%EF%BD%8A%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-f3babba57beb|archive-date = 2020-12-04|dead-url = no}}</ref>，〈如果這是情〉改編自日本搖滾樂團[[安全地帶|安全地帶]]成員[[玉置浩二|玉置浩二]]創作的歌曲〈ともだち〉，音樂短片由張文幹執導<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/DDjmOBZ.jpg|title = 人物專訪張文幹|date = 1996-06|publisher = 黎明家族會刊第二十二期|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220201025332/https://i.imgur.com/jX8FMuG.jpg|archive-date = 2022-02-01|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，填詞人[[向雪懷|向雪懷]]表示此歌曲原本選給同公司的歌手[[黃凱芹|黃凱芹]]主唱，但黃凱芹認為自己無法唱得比[[玉置浩二|玉置浩二]]好，最終把灌錄的工作交予黎明<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 史順宜 |url = https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/110810/ |title = 黎明《如果這是情》冧盡80後 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2017-08-29 |accessdate = 2021-05-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190411233109/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/110810/%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96%E6%AD%8C-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%83%85-%E5%86%A7%E7%9B%A180%E5%BE%8C-%E8%AE%93%E6%88%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A2%E6%8F%9B%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%96%E6%83%85 |archive-date = 2019-04-11 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。這張專輯在推出後約半個月，銷量已經達到十萬張以上，香港一度出現斷市情況，唱片公司需抽調準備發行海外的那批存貨，先行應付香港的訂單，並立即增加印量<ref>{{Cite web| url = https://i.imgur.com/MllpxOT.jpg|title = 一金二銀 前景美麗|author = 黎明、賈偉南 |date = 1992|publisher = 黎明回憶錄|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-02|archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220202020933/https://i.imgur.com/MllpxOT.jpg|archive-date = 2022-02-02|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

