==評論摘要==
香港傳媒工作者朱米高表示此專輯的主題曲〈親近你〉是一首中慢情歌，沿用了徐日勤作品的既定風格，副歌較為激昂，他認為徐日勤在電子合成聲效的處理上做得不錯，歌曲很有動態，而後期的混音製作亦應記一功，林夕創作的歌詞似是上一張專輯的歌曲〈無名份的浪漫〉的延續，而歌曲的前奏亦跟〈無名份的浪漫〉有少許相似，黎明當時的唱功仍屬幼嫩，聲音未開<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E8%A6%AA%E8%BF%91%E4%BD%A0-%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E4%BB%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AA%E6%BC%AB-d407fdd4cfee|title = 《親近你》延續《無名份的浪漫》|author = 朱米高|date = 2021-05-25|publisher = 千千闋歌與我常在|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220219024529/https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E8%A6%AA%E8%BF%91%E4%BD%A0-%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E4%BB%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AA%E6%BC%AB-d407fdd4cfee|archive-date = 2022-02-19|dead-url = no}}</ref>，同時認為黎明演繹歌曲〈傷心的背後〉感情豐富，有一定感染力<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%89%93%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%8C-6132eec6debd|title = 《傷心的背後》主打背後的好歌|author = 朱米高|date = 2019-08-20|publisher = 千千闋歌與我常在|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220221021404/https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%89%93%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%8C-6132eec6debd|archive-date = 202-02-21|dead-url = no}}</ref>。另一媒體則認為黎明當時的歌唱技巧雖然不足，但聲底很厚，唱歌也頗紮實，演繹〈親近你〉的唱腔與1980年代的[[張學友|張學友]]近似<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.spill.hk/overflow/leon-lai-music/ |title = 核心外圍的邊皮：如果只談黎明的音樂 |author = 王芬 |date = 2016-05-07 |publisher = Spill |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-03-20 | archive-url =http://web.archive.org/web/20211107102437/https://www.spill.hk/overflow/leon-lai-music/|archive-date =2021-11-07|dead-url =no }}</ref>。黎明對於此專輯獲得雙白金銷量感到興奮，他表示料不到有此成績<ref>{{Cite web| url = https://i.imgur.com/dVkTB1W.jpg|title = 黎明捧雙白金|date = 1992|publisher = 雜誌|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220202072746/https://i.imgur.com/dVkTB1W.jpg|archive-date = 2022-02-02|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，此成績對他來說有很大的鼓勵<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/fy2IDRO.jpg |title = 靚仔小生黎明 唱片得雙白金 他盼望可影視歌三線發展 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 18 |date = 1991-02-02|accessdate = 2021-10-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211004082440/https://i.imgur.com/fy2IDRO.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，反映出聽眾開始接受他，加強他對唱歌的信心<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/3GFhpwa.jpg |title = 黎明準備灌錄首張國語碟 |date = 1991 |publisher = 報章報導 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-05-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210515051448/https://i.imgur.com/3GFhpwa.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-15 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，他表示歡迎外界給他意見，即使是批評也樂意接受，同時認為能夠獲得別人稱讚他的歌唱技巧有進步是值得高興的事情<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |title = 黎明一年出兩唱片 未來發展投入樂壇|publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 22 |date = 1991-01-11}}</ref>。

